body_html:
Please provide details about what platform you are using (operating system, architecture). Also include your TensorFlow version. We ask for this in the issue submission template, because it is really difficult to help without that information. Thanks!

Note: The API for zeros_iniailizer was updated in recent TensorFlow versions. Much example code is written to previous TensorFlow API versions, so it is very important that you include this information. Specifically, issues like this are very unlikely to be a TensorFlow bug, but simply out of date example / model code used with a newer version of TensorFlow.
